    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/73204f08ecddea672e3694c9207f6fab.poster.avif?t=1753410576\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/73204f08ecddea672e3694c9207f6fab.webm?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/73204f08ecddea672e3694c9207f6fab.mp4?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>基于网格的回合制角色扮演</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在和乌特莫斯的对峙中战败后，我们不得不逃离了恒星系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们要和仅有的三名飞行员一起扭转这一败局。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/33db652f05f496e6e5d70c480c3ccdb7.webp?t=1753410576\" width=353 height=48 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/d35d2736550abb445021b7698a888069.poster.avif?t=1753410576\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/d35d2736550abb445021b7698a888069.webm?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/d35d2736550abb445021b7698a888069.mp4?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 打造终极战舰吧</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>各种核反应堆</strong> - 每场战争结束后都可获得可安装在战舰上的核反应堆，同时核反应堆的作用可以相互叠加使用。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>各种战舰及舰炮</strong> - 每艘战舰都装载有两个不同战斗力的舰炮，同时还可制作添加一个辅助舰炮。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/fff4160301297bed32775db6760a230a.poster.avif?t=1753410576\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/fff4160301297bed32775db6760a230a.webm?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/fff4160301297bed32775db6760a230a.mp4?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 请通过最佳路线前往恒星</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>各种任务</strong> - 战场上会出现破坏恒温箱，切断入口等多种任务，同时，暗黑地带可能会出现意想不到的事情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>各种BOSS</strong> - 守护恒星的乌特莫斯高级将领们拥有各自独有的技能，在与无法预测的BOSS们展开的战斗中，最重要的是进行明智的战略选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/d03b9cb0e0b105a3c3b5b79663ca41fd.poster.avif?t=1753410576\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/d03b9cb0e0b105a3c3b5b79663ca41fd.webm?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/d03b9cb0e0b105a3c3b5b79663ca41fd.mp4?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 不仅如此</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>回合返回</strong> - 每次战斗只有一次，我军所有战舰可恢复到回合开始的状态，同时，可发射两枚舰炮或移动两次。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>航空母舰</strong> - 航空母舰没有战斗能力。但是因为拥有时间逆时器，在任何情况下都要守护航空母舰，进行战斗。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种航空母舰的技能和强化装置</strong> - 还可以制作出对战斗有用且可以使用的航空母舰技能和强化装置。营救且部署生存者，可开放额外的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >期待大家的胜利。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/49be7608f1658a5f6c590a6bba75ff49.poster.avif?t=1753410576\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/49be7608f1658a5f6c590a6bba75ff49.webm?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365860/extras/49be7608f1658a5f6c590a6bba75ff49.mp4?t=1753410576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
